### Wallets

The wallet (aka Keychain) is where your secret key is stored. Hence, it is probably the most critical thing to be able to control.

That's why the PeerPiper Web3 Wallet is 

1. Source Code available
2. Self-hostable - Use our site, or deploy your own.

Take a look at the code, anytime. Deploy your own instance, anytime. Now THAT is Web3.0.


